8 * Unicode tables containing ranges of Unicode characters in a

12 * to be very rare in practical Ecmascript source code, and thus
13 * compactness is most important.
14 *
15 * The tables are matched using uni_range_match() and the format
16 * is described in src/extract_chars.py.
